			<div id="artTitles">
				<h1 id="artibodyTitle">《长沙走马楼三国吴简（竹简[壹]）》所见师佐籍格式复原及相关问题探讨</h1>
				<h2 id="artisubTitle"/>
			</div>
			
			<div class="articl_info">
				<div class="artBaseInfo" id="autInfo">
					<div class="articl_info_t">作 者：</div>
					<div class="articl_info_c">
						<div class="info_c">
								<a target="_blank" href="/qw?s0=4&amp;s1=%e6%b2%88%e5%88%9a">沈刚</a> 
						</div>
					</div>
					<br class="cls"/>
				</div>
				<div class="artBaseInfo" id="autDescription">
					<div class="articl_info_t">作者简介：</div>
					<div class="articl_info_c">
						<div class="info_c">沈刚，吉林大学古籍研究所。</div>
					</div>
					<br class="cls"/>
				</div>
				<div class="artBaseInfo" id="tAutInfo"/>
				<div class="artBaseInfo" id="orgInfo">
					<div class="articl_info_t">原文出处：</div>
					<div class="articl_info_c">
						<div class="info_c">人文杂志</div>
					</div>
					<br class="cls"/>
				</div>
				<div class="artBaseInfo" id="astInfo">
					<div class="articl_info_t">内容提要：</div>
					<div class="articl_info_c">
						<div class="info_c">
							<p>本文对走马楼吴简中师佐籍的格式进行了重新复原，区分出右类和凡类的不同，认为师佐名籍是两次编成。师佐是由郡、县两级地方政府负责管理，但分工各有不同。政府在每年八月编制师佐籍总帐。师佐及其家属名籍的编制反映了孙吴政权对手工业管理者控制之严格。师佐集中在郡中的工官中，其社会地位在政治和经济两个方面表现不平衡。</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<br class="cls"/>
				</div>
				<div id="artPdcInfo" class="artBaseInfo">
					<div class="col_info"><b>期刊代号：</b>K22 </div>
					<div class="col_info"><b>分类名称：</b>魏晋南北朝隋唐史 </div>
					<div class="col_info"><b>复印期号：</b>2009 年 02 期 </div>
					<br class="cls"/>
				</div>
				<div class="artBaseInfo" id="artKeyword">
					<div class="articl_info_t">关 键 词：</div>
					<div class="articl_info_c">
						<div class="info_c">
								<a target="_blank" href="/qw?s0=7&amp;s1=%e5%b8%88%e4%bd%90">师佐</a> 
								<a target="_blank" href="/qw?s0=7&amp;s1=%e8%b5%b0%e9%a9%ac%e6%a5%bc">走马楼</a> 
								<a target="_blank" href="/qw?s0=7&amp;s1=%e6%a0%bc%e5%bc%8f">格式</a> 

						</div>
